function redirectPage(pageUrl)
{
//alert(pageUrl);
	var currentURL = window.location.href;

	var baseURL    = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL.toLowerCase().lastIndexOf("pages"));    

	baseURL        = baseURL + "Pages/" + pageUrl;
//alert(baseURL);
	
	window.location = baseURL;
}


function redirectExternal(pageUrl, isHttp)
{
	if(isHttp)
		pageUrl = "http://" + pageUrl;
	else
		pageUrl = "https://" + pageUrl;
	
	
	window.open(pageUrl, '_blank');
}

(function(){

        if (typeof(_spBodyOnLoadFunctions) === 'undefined' || _spBodyOnLoadFunctions === null) {
            return;
        }
        _spBodyOnLoadFunctions.push(function() 
        {
          ExecuteOrDelayUntilScriptLoaded(
            function()
            {
              var pairs = SP.ScriptHelpers.getDocumentQueryPairs();
              var followDoc, itemId, listId, docName;
              for (var key in pairs)
              {
                if(key.toLowerCase() == 'followdocument') 
                  followDoc = pairs[key];
                else if(key.toLowerCase() == 'itemid') 
                  itemId = pairs[key];
                else if(key.toLowerCase() == 'listid') 
                  listId = pairs[key];

                  docName = decodeURI(pairs[key]);

                  FollowDocumentFromEmail(itemId, listId, docName);
                });
              }

            }, 'SP.init.js');

        });

                    myDocsActionsMenuPopulator(renderCtx, calloutActionMenu);

                    CalloutOnPostRenderTemplate(renderCtx, calloutActionMenu);

           <script>
            function OnPressEnter(e) {

        if (e.keyCode == 13 && ValidateUserControl("lgn")) {

            ValidateLogin();
        }
    }

    function ValidateLogin() {

        var uidVal = document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_txtUserName').value;
        var pwdVal = document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_txtPassword').value;
        

        if (ValidateUserControl("lgn")) {

            var siteURL = "/sites/sro/" + "_layouts/15/SRO/LoginValidation.aspx";
            showSpinner();
            $.ajax({
                url: siteURL,
                type: 'POST',
                dataType: 'json',
                data: {
                    uid: uidVal,
                    pwd: pwdVal,
                },
                success: function (data) {
                    if (data.result == 'success') {
                        try {
                            //$("#addEdit").modal('hide');
                            hideSpinner();
                            document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_lblError').style.display = 'none';
                    //location.reload();
                    location.href = '/sites/sro/Pages/InternetBooking/User/MyProfile.aspx';
                }
                catch (err) {
                    $(".spinnerWrapper").delay(2000).fadeOut(20);
                    $("#" + 'ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_divBeforeLogin').attr('class', 'dropdown open');
                        document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_lblError').style.display = 'inline';
                    }
                }
                else {
                    hideSpinner();
                    $("#" + 'ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_divBeforeLogin').attr('class', 'dropdown open');
                    document.getElementById('ctl00_g_22827a12_2509_4ca9_8ae8_5fa0cf94e89b_ctl00_ctl00_lblError').style.display = 'inline';
            }
        },
        error: function (data) {
            console.warn("some error happend, possibly backend service is not responding", data);
            hideSpinner();
        }
    });
}
    return false;
}
           </script>

                   UCQuickSearch = {
        EnableReturnTripSelection: function (enable) {
            if (enable === true) {
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").removeAttr("disabled");
               
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_cvDatesValidator");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);
                EnableCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpReturnDate', true);

                //Added to set departure class as return class also - CH1
                var value = $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlDepartureClass").val();
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").val(value);

            } else {
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").change();
              
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_cvDatesValidator");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);
                EnableCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpReturnDate', false);
                ResetCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpReturnDate');

                //Reset Return  - CH2
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").val('');
            }
        },

        ResetFields: function () {

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbOneWay").iCheck('check');


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlFrom").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlFrom").change();

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlTo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlTo").change();

            ResetCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpDepartureDate');

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlDepartureClass").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlDepartureClass").change();


            ResetCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpReturnDate');

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlReturnClass").change();

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").val('1');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").val('0');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").val('0');


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_chkFlexibleDates").attr('checked', false);
        },




        InitialiseSettings: function () {
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").val('1');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").val('0');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").val('0');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").css("display", "none");
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").css("display", "none");
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").css("display", "none");


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlAdults").on('change', function () {

                var ddlAdults = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlAdults");
                var selectedText = ddlAdults.options[ddlAdults.selectedIndex].innerHTML;

                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").val(selectedText);
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").attr('readOnly', 'true');
            });

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlChildren").on('change', function () {

                var ddlChildren = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlChildren");
                var selectedText = ddlChildren.options[ddlChildren.selectedIndex].innerHTML;

                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").val(selectedText);
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").attr('readOnly', 'true');
            });


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlInfants").on('change', function () {
                var ddlInfants = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_ddlInfants");
                var selectedText = ddlInfants.options[ddlInfants.selectedIndex].innerHTML;
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").val(selectedText);
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").attr('readOnly', 'true');

            });


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbOneWay").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',
                increaseArea: '20%' // optional
            });


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbRoundtrip").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',
                increaseArea: '20%' // optional
            });

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_chkFlexibleDates").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',
                increaseArea: '20%' // optional
            });


            // rbOneWay.checked function 
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbOneWay").on('ifChecked', function (event) {
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbOneWay").attr('checked', true);
                UCQuickSearch.EnableReturnTripSelection(false);


            });

            // rbRoundtrip.checked function 
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbRoundtrip").on('ifChecked', function (event) {
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbRoundtrip").attr('checked', true);
                UCQuickSearch.EnableReturnTripSelection(true);

            });


            // init fields 
            if ($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbOneWay").is(":checked")) {
                UCQuickSearch.EnableReturnTripSelection(false);
            }
            else if ($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_rbRoundtrip").is(":checked")) {
                UCQuickSearch.EnableReturnTripSelection(true);
            }


            $(function () {

                /// when the user selects departure date, then allow the user to select only the dates that comes after the departure date
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpDepartureDate_txtSelectedDate").datepicker("option", "onClose", function (selectedDate) {
                    $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_dpReturnDate_txtSelectedDate").datepicker("option", "minDate", selectedDate);
                    $(this).blur();
                });

                 

            });
        }

    function cvMaxAllowedPassengerCount_ClientValidate(sender, arguments) {

        arguments.IsValid = true;

        var AdultsCount = parseInt($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults").val());
        var ChildrenCount = parseInt($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren").val());
        var InfantsCount = parseInt($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants").val());

        var sum = AdultsCount + ChildrenCount + InfantsCount;
        if (sum > parseInt('12')) {
            arguments.IsValid = false;
        }

        if (arguments.IsValid == false) {
            if (AdultsCount > 0) {
                AddErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults"));
            }
            else {
                RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults"));
            }

            if (ChildrenCount > 0) {
                AddErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren"));
            }
            else {
                RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren"));
            }


            if (InfantsCount > 0) {
                AddErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants"));
            }
            else {
                RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants"));
            }
        }
        else {
            RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtAdults"));
            RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtChildren"));
            RemoveErrorClass($("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl00_txtInfants"));
        }

    }

        ResetFields: function () {
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbStation").iCheck('check');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');
            ResetCalendar('ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_dpDepartureDate');
        },
        EnableTrainSelection: function (enable) {

            if (enable === true) {

                // enable ddlSearchTrainNo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").removeAttr("disabled");

                // enable rfvSearchTrainNo
                var oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchTrainNo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);


                // disable ddlSearchStationFrom
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');

                // disable rfvSearchStationFrom
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationFrom");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);

                // disable ddlSearchStationTo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');

                // disable rfvSearchStationTo
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationTo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);

            } else {

                // disable ddlSearchTrainNo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchTrainNo").find('option:first').attr('selected', 'selected');

                // disable rfvSearchTrainNo
                var oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchTrainNo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, false);


                // enable ddlSearchStationFrom
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationFrom").removeAttr("disabled");

                // enable rfvSearchStationFrom
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationFrom");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);

                // enable ddlSearchStationTo
                $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_ddlSearchStationTo").removeAttr("disabled");

                // enable rfvSearchStationTo
                oVal = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rfvSearchStationTo");
                ValidatorEnable(oVal, true);

            }
        },

        InitialiseSettings: function () {
            // init Train Status fields

            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbStation").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',

            });


            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbTrainNumber").iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'icheckbox_square-orange',
                radioClass: 'iradio_square-orange',
                increaseArea: '20%' // optional
            });


            // rbStation.checked function 
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbStation").on('ifChecked', function (event) {

                UCTrainStatus.EnableTrainSelection(false);

            });

            // rbTrainNumber.checked function 
            $("#ctl00_ctl36_g_4f30100f_8b3e_4277_8604_9a1c4e6767e0_ctl03_rbTrainNumber").on('ifChecked', function (event) {

                UCTrainStatus.EnableTrainSelection(true);


            });

            // init fields 
            UCTrainStatus.EnableTrainSelection(false);


           // Comment out by Hassan to show whole month dates of future
           

        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {

        UCTrainStatus.InitialiseSettings();
    });
                  </script>
